        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/e9bcb4/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2018-01-23T16:11:31.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Matthew King\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n Matthew King:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>I hope people don\u2019t take your thoughtful and detailed tasting notes here for granted.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>I believe that there is little risk of that.  I expect that, for good reason, Jeremy\u2019s notes are among the most viewed on the board.  For me, even being ITB, the challenge is finding common experience such that I can offer anything substantive in a reply.  However, that does not keep me from reading and appreciating every one.  Thank you, Jeremy.</p>",
